&lt;p&gt;At Trivelta, we build the technology that powers modern iGaming experiences, partnering with online sports betting and casino operators to launch fully customised, branded, and legally compliant platforms that drive engagement, retention, and revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Partnership Manager, you will be responsible for building and managing relationships with casino content providers and aggregators that form a key part of our technology platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will manage these relationships end-to-end, from initial identification and negotiation through to onboarding oversight and ongoing performance management. You will be the main point of contact for casino partners, ensuring commercial agreements remain competitive and integrations run smoothly. You will ensure Trivelta&#39;s content offering remains competitive, diverse, and compliant, working closely with the best studios and aggregators in the market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and manage relationships with casino content providers, aggregators, and RNG-certified game studios&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the onboarding of new casino partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate and manage commercial agreements, revenue share models, and contractual terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor partner performance and identify opportunities to optimise content mix&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on market trends, emerging providers, and the competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Trivelta at industry events and maintain a strong network within the iGaming ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideally 2+ years of experience in partnerships, business development, or account management, procurement or a similar commercial role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to negotiate and manage commercial agreementsStrong relationship management skills and comfortable managing multiple partners in a fast-moving environmentBased in or willing to relocate to BarcelonaFluent English required; an additional language is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open to occasional travel to industry events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No visa sponsorship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is hybrid based out of our Barcelona office located near la Barceloneta.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Trivelta&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Trivelta builds the technology that powers modern, social-first gaming experiences. Through our proprietary sweepstakes-based sportsbook and casino engine, we enable partners to launch their own fully branded, legally compliant gaming products. Our flagship consumer app, ReBet, demonstrates the power of the Trivelta platform, combining real social interactions, predictive gameplay, and casino entertainment in one unified experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Headquartered in Boston with operations in Monterrey, Barcelona, and Atlanta, we&#39;re scaling rapidly and building a team passionate about redefining how people play, bet, and connect online.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;We are looking for a QA Engineer to be the last line of defense on quality across our sportsbook and casino platform. You will work closely with developers, product managers, and designers to catch what others miss and give the team the confidence to ship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Design, write, and execute detailed manual test cases for sportsbook features (pre-match and in-play betting, bet slips, cash-out, odds display, settlement) and casino games (slots, table games, live dealer).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Perform functional, regression, exploratory, UI/UX, cross-browser, and cross-device testing across web, iOS, and Android.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Verify the accuracy of odds, payouts, bet settlement, bonuses, free bets, and promotional mechanics down to the last decimal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Test deposit, withdrawal, and payment journeys across multiple providers and currencies, validating transaction integrity end to end.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Log clear, reproducible bug reports with precise steps, evidence, and severity; track defects through to resolution and retest fixes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Validate responsible gaming controls, including deposit limits, self-exclusion, reality checks, and age/identity verification, and confirm compliance with regulatory and licensing requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
