&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with product managers and engineers to define requirements, edge cases, and acceptance criteria early&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embed automated testing into our CI/CD pipeline to support rapid, confident releases&lt;/li&gt;
