&lt;li&gt;A proactive, ownership-driven mindset—you see problems and fix them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Startup or early-stage company experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud infrastructure (AWS, GCP, or Azure)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to performance or load testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with microservices, event-driven systems, or data-heavy applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to influence quality culture beyond just test execution&lt;/li&gt;
