&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High-Volume Recruitment&lt;/strong&gt;: Lead end-to-end recruitment for studio-based talent, including hosts, presenters, and customer-facing roles. Build strong candidate pipelines and maintain momentum to support rapid team expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
